Electronic Community Health Information System Monthly Report - May 2023

Ministry of Health

This is a monthly statistical update generated with data from the electronic Community Health Information System. This system is currently deployed in 9 districts, supporting 2,912 VHTs as seen below.

Achievements in May 2023

  • National Training of Trainers for 60 master trainers in Jinja
  • District Health Team Trainings for 50 DHTs in Ntugamo and 40 in Lamwo
  • Onboarding of 801 VHTs on to eCHIS in Ntugamo Districts.
  • Integration of the WASH MIS into eCHIS.
  • Refresher Trainings in all West Nile, Lango, and Acholi
  • Pilot of the Translated eCHIS in Buikwe.
  • Review of the Immunisation Workflows in eCHIS.
  • CHT Stakeholders Engagements
  • OpenSRP user acceptance Test held in Soroti.

State of the eCHIS Roll Out
